{"tid":1840414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家要做既 係同醫護企係同一陣線 而唔係推佢地去孤島","createTime":"2020-01-24T21:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T22:30:59.000Z","uid":33786,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96e8c5e91352fbda3315afa28228748e390dc8b1","tid":1840414,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:24:11.000Z","msg":"比起大家自己唔係做醫護既 叫人地罷工就緊係易<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既唔應該係單方面叫醫護自己一個孤獨咁罷<br />\n<br />\n憑咩我地可以獨善其身 由得醫護自己罷工?<br />\n<br />\n我地大家都係香港人 要罷就一撚齊罷 憑咩要醫護自己一個攬哂上身?<br />\n<br />\n人多就係力量 香港人要罷既 就一齊罷<br />\n<br />\n天滅中共之餘 香港人亦都要齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落 唔係口號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53b705345fa532d67da90c9983ec6e7e01c39c6","tid":1840414,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:24:27.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落 唔係口號"},{"pid":"b02a84149e99108d78557652049298a60b941c8f","tid":1840414,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0296ce97d5f4936c7b26ad966cca8829638b5051","tid":1840414,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c367927e86fd6bf98bd83f6d63da6d74be8ea613","tid":1840414,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:29:14.000Z","msg":"幫手輕輕推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32fd4f0f4fd0b48a53f142ac079d8ca4c30e4af","tid":1840414,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"770ce02baa85c06bcd972e6cdafec04ee7468dee","tid":1840414,"uid":33786,"like